{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>李家鼎（鼎爺）前妻施明的喪禮將於今日（4月22日）於大圍寶福紀念館設靈，翌日大殮儀式結束後，靈柩隨即奉移富山火化場火化。李泳豪與父親李家鼎以及太太Agnes於下午4時左右抵達寶福紀念館，可是靈堂門外有工作人員攔住了他們，並不讓Agnes進靈堂內，她需要在靈堂外等候。問到Agnes有什麼想跟奶奶說，工作人員代答：「佢喺心入面講咗。」再問Agnes會否好失望？工作人員又代答說：「無回應，唔接受訪問。（Agnes有無咩同奶奶講？）要講都講咗喇。」問到Agnes可有懷念奶奶的往事，是否也很錫奶奶 ，可會覺得很委屈？她一律沒有回應，連眼神都沒有任何示意。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123661941295288320542613.jpeg/weyCHn2P3rHio6e2YLZMyVYEaSIoSCpiUpNu42STbuM\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123661938543693824803247.jpeg/zfdFk1yyog9K4Yt5YobtQdKSB6uc8x5u_iarwcgmq8E\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123661935997620224051479.jpeg/YAGtXpJI1WWj5iJbkwCHarWlMn82pv_dB_DS7THw0u0\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123661933141168128267419.jpeg/6Bty8w2rddvchob3Ys8CI8ELDO3lSOFsGoCeXiyAnl4\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123661930427322368236409.jpeg/jDcN86HcWmBA1V6oujbbfgRL4JgNjvuNRqcHXXCnB10\" alt=\"靈堂外向奶奶鞠躬。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>靈堂外向奶奶鞠躬。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123662335785832448462958.jpeg/Nws3xzSS6Xe9d7Ru0fFpE7gsYPoXhIWEMshj0gTIY9I\"></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T08:45:51.437130+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":319,"images":6,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}